  <entry>
    <title>【PC】根神京都姬骑士 后编</title>
    <link href="https://yinghu.netlify.app/posts/4dc13205.html"/>
    <id>https://yinghu.netlify.app/posts/4dc13205.html</id>
    <published>2024-05-13T01:38:50.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-05-13T01:51:42.034Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>人烟绝迹，被寂静笼罩的京都之街。</p><p>数日之前，在受卖命撕心裂肺的呼喊声中，涟离开了村子。另一方面，为应对妖怪的进攻，都部转移了据点。<br>而于现下，涟出现在东云面前，并扬言“杀了你之后，就去杀了瑠华。”<br>妖怪与宫内机关的战斗。在那背后暗涌的策谋和真相。<br>涟的真意。东云的决意。受卖命的真心。瑠华的奢望。</p><p>在生命飘零中，少女们所描绘的是无不为之爱怜的存在——公主与姬骑士。<br>而最终，迎接她们的结局是……</p><hr><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%60%E3%80%90%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E3%80%91/%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96galgame%E4%BC%9A%E7%A4%BE%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96%E4%BC%9A%E7%A4%BE%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%20part28/%E9%BB%92%E5%BD%A9%E9%BB%84%E6%B3%89%E8%B7%AF/%5B200512%5D%5B%E9%BB%92%E5%BD%A9%E9%BB%84%E6%B3%89%E8%B7%AF%5D%20%E3%81%AD%E3%81%AE%E3%81%8B%E3%81%BF%20%E4%BA%AC%E3%81%AE%E9%83%BD%E3%81%A8%E3%81%B5%E3%81%9F%E3%82%8A%E3%81%AE%E5%A7%AB%E9%A8%8E%E5%A3%AB%20%E5%BE%8C%E7%B7%A8%20steam%E7%89%88%20(files).rar"   title="点击下载"><i class="red larger"></i><span>点击下载</span></a>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
